    "body" : "<p><strong>Kotlin Answer</strong></p>\n<p>Get first key then get value of key. Kotlin has &quot;<em><strong>first()</strong></em>&quot; function:</p>\n<pre><code>val list = HashMap&lt;String, String&gt;() // Dummy HashMap.\n\nval keyFirstElement = list.keys.first() // Get key.\n\nval valueOfElement = list.getValue(keyFirstElement) // Get Value.\n</code></pre>\n"
